Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,One Dream One Wish
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,kanaetai nara Over The Top
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to make it\Ncome true, Over The Top
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,ONE PIECE - LAND OF WANO ARC
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,mitakoto mo nai sekai mezashi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Setting out into the unknown world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,araburu namikaze koete
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Weathering rough wind and waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to keep going because\NI want to get there first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,tsukisusumanakya dame sa\Nichibannori shitain da
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Worry later since it's\Nall sink or swim anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,shinpai toka atomawashi\Ndouse shoubu ichika bachika
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When your opponent looks daunting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,aite ga dekaku mietara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sign that your heart is shrinking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,kokoro ga chijinderu shouko
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Running away is not a choice
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,nigeru nante choisu wa nai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Take one step closer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,ippo soba e chikadukun da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Being called insolent's a compliment, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,namaiki tte homekotoba?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When things become tough,\Nthat's when you should laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,kitsui toki hodo warattoke
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to look for a new tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,atarashii ashita sagashi ni ikitai no nara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Polish your unique confidence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,tobikkiri no jishin wo migaite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Until your footsteps
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,tabi wo shita ashiato ga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Become a map
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,sou! chizu ni kawaru made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A new horizon, look, how far you've come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,atarashii Horizon hora susunde kita bun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's brighter and the\Nlevel of difficulty rises
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,mabushisa to nanido ga joushou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,yumeutsutsu de okose Hurricane
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Live in your dream and raise a hurricane
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,saa! chaato kakimidase
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Stir up the rankings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,One Dream One Wish
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,yume wa nigenai... zenbu Knock out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreams don't run away... Knock everything out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.18,0:02:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Over The Top
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's next?!\NThey're not even a good enough warm up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You stole my sword, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not your sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a weapon collector?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do with all those?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We happen to need a lot of weapons, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your weapon collection...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take the whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will bring you down instead,\Nyou damn mountain bandit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry if I confused you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Gyukimaru!\NZoro Fights a Duel on Bandit's Bridge!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat the red-bean soup already...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, haven't we reached\Nthe place called Udon yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopperemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me drooling like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be long, Olin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we get to Udon,\Nwe'll save Big Bro Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...we'll eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...the red-bean soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Otama-chan, do you like it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was treated to it by Otsuru-san\Non my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My mouth slowly filled with\Nthe sweetness of the red-bean paste...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My taste buds were truly dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Red-bean paste is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes! Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh! Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Red-bean paste! And a rice cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had such a soft and delicious thing\Nin my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A white rice cake shines\Nlike a living frog's eyeball!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A frog's eyeball?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Olin-chan, that's a little freaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah? Just by thinking about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help drooling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not edible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to have the red-bean soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They are getting quite excited\Ntalking about the red-bean soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Once she finds out there's no red-bean soup,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the shock might bring back her memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and she'll return to herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of saving him,\Nwe'll put Luffy in harm's way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?!\NWhat am I supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,--Bring me more red-bean soup!\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffytaro wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, Luffytaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:07:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee... You took down all the Pleasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's not it? You won again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Rayleigh was doing it effortlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rayleigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When you use the Haki of the Color of Arms,\Nimagine you're wearing invisible armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,At that moment, Rayleigh sent the elephant flying\Nwithout touching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The first Haki he showed me was\Na very high level one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can use that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...Grizzly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...Magnum!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take down Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's taking too much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you let me do it,\Nthe execution will be done in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't really understand\Nhow the Sumo Inferno works!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The length of the fight
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and the number of opponents.\NThose are the toughest elements in fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll lose his spirit and energy little by little\Nand die miserably.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"The execution will be done in no time"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not exciting at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a refill!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?! You've already had\Nso much red-bean soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you!\NRed-bean soup is like oxygen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No one else can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My red-bean soup! It's my favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Send my opponent flying\Nas if I'm wearing invisible armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw hat man, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna practice! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your next opponents are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Gifters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't miss any secret talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bat Smile Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bat-man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The beautiful leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a swift runner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Gazelle Smile Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Gazelle-man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the Gifters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! There are two Gifters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They kidnapped Tama, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you mess with Holdem-sama\Nand Bakura Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! They're perfect sparring partners!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Lock eyes with your opponents!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful Leg Spin Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just an ordinary punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it right this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's invisible armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Invisible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner is Luffytaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This Straw Hat is quite strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm... That wasn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not supposed to touch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could try something more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I met Ryuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You met Ryuma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I believe such nonsense?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the soul belonged to\Nsomeone else I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking gibberish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you know Ryuma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuma is a great swordsman\Nwho was said to cut any opponent in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not know how valuable\Nthe great sword Shusui is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shusui is the Land of Wano's treasure!\NIt belongs to Ryuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, when the Land of Wano
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,was recognized as the Land\Nof Gold by other countries...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Unguarded!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates around the world wanted gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobles tried to rule\Nthe Land of Gold - the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He showed those enemies from overseas\Nhow formidable he was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and burned the Land of Wano's samurai\Nin their minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That is who Ryuma is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many legends related to him\Nas a swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...says that he slayed a dragon\Nthat appeared above the capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,After his death, he was laid to rest in a temple\Nwith the great sword Shusui...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...as this country's God of the Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shusui is a national treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But it has nothing to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take back Shusui!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel comfortable\Nwith just two swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I have overestimated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shusui is a Black Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it was forged\Nthrough the battles that Ryuma fought!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only trying to figure\Nout if you were a punk
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,with no backbone who just wanted to have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Forged"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I was wondering about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that Black Blades are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Unguarded!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try your best to catch me off guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Catching people off guard is the only way to\Nwin deadly battles, so that is all I am trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody, help!\NSomeone is trying to kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's a samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they serious or just fooling around?\NI can't tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Swordsmen, please help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they're not joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Unguarded!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you wait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you, take a hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Our duel is not over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight you! But could you wait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the murderer - Zorojuro, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A WANTED PERSON IN THE FLOWER CAPITAL
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,HITOKIRI KAMAZO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Zorojuro, why would you\Nwanna help that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you wanna slash a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only trying to kill that brat\Nwho won't stop laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Toko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitokiri Kamazo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a street slasher\Nwho randomly kills people in the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're actually an assassin working for Orochi\Nwhile disguised as an outlaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, why would you want to kill Otoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You address the Shogun, Orochi-sama,\Nwith no honorific.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Samurai-sama, please help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course, I'm not gonna just stand here\Nand watch a kid and a woman get killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give you anything you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sake and food would be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem. I've been told that I can kill\Nas many as I want if they get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:21:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I often get in trouble afterwards\Nwhen I slay someone who has a boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be the one dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's quite strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.04,0:22:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're getting serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Against the two formidable opponents,\NKamazo and Gyukimaru, Zoro wields only two swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The fierce scramble drives him into a corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Facing the worst crisis ever without Shusui,\Nhe risks his life and takes the chance of a lifetime!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.80,0:23:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Big Turnover! The Three-Sword\NStyle Overcomes Danger!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.95,0:23:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
